OL,5, Ukraine's recapture of the city of     
OL,6, Izyum has brought multiple allegations 
OL,7, of atrocities under Russian occupation.
OL,8, Among the accounts emerging is that of 
OL,9, a group of Sri Lankans held captive for
OL,10, months. Here, they tell their story.   
OL,12,F"We thought we would never get out     
OL,13,Falive," says Dilujan Paththinajakan,   
OL,15,FDilujan was one of seven Sri Lankans   
OL,16,Fcaptured by Russian forces in May. The 
OL,17,Fgroup had just set out on a huge walk  
OL,18,Fto safety from their homes in Kupiansk,
OL,19,Fnorth-eastern Ukraine, to the relative 
OL,20,Fsafety of Kharkiv, some 120km (75      
OL,21,Fmiles) away.                           
